java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
public class ValueMap
extends java.util.AbstractMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>

Map implementation that exposes the properties of a FacesBean as a Map. This Map supports Iterator.remove(), treats putting a null value as identical to removing the value, but does not support null keys. The keys may be either Strings or PropertyKeys, but all Map.Entry objects will return String keys.
